===Etymology===
First attested in 1541.<ref name=CH/> {{bor|en|frm|abdomen}}, from {{der|en|la|abdomen}}, possibly from {{m|la|abdō||conceal}}, from {{m|la|ab||away}} + {{m|la|dere||to put, place}}.<ref name=CH>{{R:CDOE|page=2}}</ref>

